import filesMutations from './files'

  ...accountMutations,
  ...casesMutations,
  ...filesMutations,
  ...viewerMutations,
  ...snapshotMutations,
  ...teamManagerMutations,
  ...searchMutations,
  ...relatedFind,
  ...logs,
  ...diagnosis,
  ...clinicianView
}
